\pard\f0\fs28  Subgen.{\b  Galeopsis}. Vegetative parts and usually also bracteoles and calyx with rigid, yellowish hairs and glandular hairs, sometimes with appressed hairs; stem 4-angled, more or less swollen at the nodes.
\par

